{"id":310702,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/维权网-参加黑农垦违法研讨会者遭拘押，刘杰传/","date":"2013-08-26T14:18:10Z","modified":"2013-08-26T14:18:10Z","title":"维权网 | 参加黑农垦违法研讨会者遭拘押，刘杰传出控诉信（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员雷鸣报道）今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日）本网信息员接到黑龙江农垦维权代表刘杰从看守所中辗转传出的控诉信，揭露黑龙江农垦抓捕参加北京就农垦集团违法违宪举行的研讨会成员，以及农垦公安违法粗暴审讯维权人士的情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘杰是从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>号从北京被押回软禁，到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>点钟被北安公安分局警察上门抓走，审讯到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日，警方以“</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">29</span><span>日至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">31</span><span>日，逊克农场居民刘杰在互联网自己的腾讯微博（网名护宪卫士）上，两次发贴子称‘逊克农场管理区杜建华、孙绍全等干部象黑社会，不交钱就抢粮’，捏造事实诽谤他人，给受害人造成不良社会影响”，将刘杰行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天。但是，在刘杰关押期间，农垦警方审讯刘杰却始终围绕着北京召开的农垦研讨会。警方利用各种污蔑、污辱的语言来激怒刘杰，警方公然说胡星斗教授参与关注农垦违法问题是为了钱。警方如此等等庸俗下流语言与方式，使得刘杰一度气昏过去。刘杰一度受到长期间的审讯与谩骂，使她心身倍受折磨，几次到医院救治。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘杰到看守所中看到与自己一起参加北京揭露农垦黑幕研讨会的另两名农垦职工刘玉云、赵丽华也被关押在看守所中。由此可见，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月底参加北京揭露黑龙江农垦研讨会的黑龙江农垦维权职工应该全部被农垦当局拘押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘杰到</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日拘留期满后，又被警方变更为涉嫌“寻衅滋事罪”刑事拘留。由此可见，黑龙江农垦当局肆意打压刘杰等维权人士关注揭露农垦黑幕，以期掩盖农垦违法侵权的制度与罪恶的行径。值得各界高度关注！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1zLu5PCnxhw/UhtSr-_TlgI/AAAAAAAAnVc/OYMwqDXEXW8/s1600/%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-1zLu5PCnxhw/UhtSr-_TlgI/AAAAAAAAnVc/OYMwqDXEXW8/s320/%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5D1JAIy8Y_o/UhtSvhq14RI/AAAAAAAAnVk/j0R9uh4KXOs/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+001.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-5D1JAIy8Y_o/UhtSvhq14RI/AAAAAAAAnVk/j0R9uh4KXOs/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+001.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fqBDt0Ox8SY/UhtS0sMHE7I/AAAAAAAAnVs/hmBWeW5Xx1c/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+002.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fqBDt0Ox8SY/UhtS0sMHE7I/AAAAAAAAnVs/hmBWeW5Xx1c/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+002.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-SWpbwC5ahOQ/UhtS9tTYQrI/AAAAAAAAnWE/Ff5iYFQq9PQ/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+003.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-SWpbwC5ahOQ/UhtS9tTYQrI/AAAAAAAAnWE/Ff5iYFQq9PQ/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+003.jpg\" width=\"234\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CRcCOsc4Ees/UhtS1fRFzxI/AAAAAAAAnV0/FxU15K5ATO4/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+004.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-CRcCOsc4Ees/UhtS1fRFzxI/AAAAAAAAnV0/FxU15K5ATO4/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+004.jpg\" width=\"232\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-t2POtcjatrk/UhtTF_w4sOI/AAAAAAAAnWM/8XbtHkyRRzQ/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+005.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-t2POtcjatrk/UhtTF_w4sOI/AAAAAAAAnWM/8XbtHkyRRzQ/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+005.jpg\" width=\"230\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TVnXdtLVGbs/UhtS6z2DYLI/AAAAAAAAnV8/Wb5msr-Tij0/s1600/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+006.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TVnXdtLVGbs/UhtS6z2DYLI/AAAAAAAAnV8/Wb5msr-Tij0/s320/%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6+006.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}